<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.1">
<l>poṟuttēṉpuṉ colneñ cilporuḷiṉpa meṉaviraṇṭum</l>
<l>iṟuttēṉaim pulaṉkaṭ kaṭaṉāyiṉa vāyiloṭṭi</l>
<l>yaṟuttēṉār vañceṟṟa mavaitaṉṉaima ṉattakaṟṟi</l>
<l>veṟuttēṉniṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In [my] heart, I tolerated vile words; I paid with both wealth and pleasures</l>
<l>The toll that was to [my] five senses. [Then] assailing my sense organs,</l>
<l>I rooted out desire and anger. Banishing them from my mind,</l>
<l>I renounced [all]. I took refuge in you, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
